Output neofetch.svg
Set Theme github-dark

Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set EmbedFont examples/fonts/SourceCodePro-Regular.woff2
Set FontSize 22
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1300
Set Height 800
Set Scroll false
Set LineHeight 1

Type "neofetch"

Sleep 500ms

Enter

Sleep 2s

Type "Welcome to DVD!"

Sleep 1s

Space

Type "A tool for generating terminal SVGs from code."

Sleep 1s